Dude ...you Rock...I was waiting for this for 5 years now...
Thanks

Yeah. I got tired of waiting also. I guess they feel it's too political. Like Victoria, after she went batshit crazy after 9-11, they removed even her jokes.com videos, and buried the episode. I had hoped I had it recorded on a tape somewhere, but I haven't come across it. I don't know why they won't run Marc's though. I bought it from Amazon.com.
